function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

id_Self = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()

Hydra.ActorPlayConversation("QST_Hawe_Delta_Zurke_07", id_Self, npc_Zurke_POI_01)
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

actorZurke01 = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(npc_Zurke_POI_01)
	
	if (Hydra.ActorIsValid(actorZurke01)) then
		Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(actorZurke01)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(actorZurke01, npc_Zurke_POI_02, "NPC_WALK", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(actorZurke01, npc_Zurke_POI_02)
		Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(actorZurke01, "NPC_Zurke_Idle_Channel")
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(actorZurke01)
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(actorZurke01)
	end

end
